{"tid":1221242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湯家驊：不反對擱置修例　政府應考慮不同方案","createTime":"2019-06-14T07:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T09:16:52.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b50b8857f7dd41b1977670d97aa4e6ebfc8fc057","tid":1221242,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:10:33.000Z","msg":"一直支持修例的湯家驊接受《蘋果》查詢時指，若不想見到有人再受傷害，政府便要考慮不同的可行方案：「我嘅意見係：特區政府盡量去考慮所有唔同嘅方案，唔應該排除任何方案。<br />\n<br />\n呢啲方案係包括唔係即時去通過呢條條例」，換言之包括暫緩通過。<br />\n<br />\n記者問他個人傾向採用甚麼方案時，湯家驊回應時暗示行會曾作討論：「我唔可以披露我哋行會嘅討論，我只可以講，所有可行方案，政府都應該考慮。」記者追問行會是否曾就此開會，湯家驊強調不能披露。"},{"pid":"e9622eaec0d5efa0e6aae1bc1d0a1581fae68f74","tid":1221242,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:10:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190614/59713739\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190614%2F59713739&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpAUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=7ec3975f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190614%2F59713739&h=7a80873c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190614/59713739</a>"},{"pid":"103f4ac3ee9080283c67a7029c9671ef7953d7a4","tid":1221242,"uid":22131,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:13:20.000Z","msg":"十一哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87117057d876244a097b4fd9d7af5c1da13c1e13","tid":1221242,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae1cc8ef996cfa66c9bc62dbf8d0b91e30f77ad","tid":1221242,"uid":231040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:14:38.000Z",